extendedInfo.description: 50+ awesome filters, upload photo to facebook, export photo to memory card and lot more you can do with Photorect. Photorect filters digitally enhance your photos to look more attractive and awesome. Features:- Filters: categorized as followsEffect - overall enhances your photo quality and make it look better than original. Border - borders will create frame around your photos to look more attractivepatterns - a more textural look to your photoAction - set of filters selected by us which would be combination of above three categories (effects, borders and patterns). You can use these effects for quick actions or else you can filter your photo manually by selecting any filters from the above categories in combination.- Upload to Facebook: after applying filters on the photo you can upload the same to Facebook- Export to memory card: you also have choice to export photo to memory cardGive it a try and if you like it then please review about it. If you are facing any problem then you can email me at gmerchant.sameer@gmail.com.Photorect is in no way endorsed by Facebook.
